metadata.description:
To move the frog:
・Click or tap the direction.
・Use arrow keys or WASD keys.
・Leave it for a few moments.

This NFT is about interactive content using WebGL, not 3D model (gltf).

After start playing the content, the 3D model of the frog is loaded separately from IPFS storage. The frog will not appear until it is completed. Also, if something goes wrong, the frog would not appear.

Behavior and appearance may vary depending on the environment (device, browser). It possibly stop working in the future due to WebGL or other factors.

This content was exported by Godot 3.4.2.
The actual location is below and please check the README.txt for additional information.
https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmYZzLPQCfLx8KaM24AYJDYPixfusTwn4Ds2ee74w2eAUn
